               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280221-132-cd700" type="crimeDate">31st of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280221-132-off699 t18280221-132-cd700"></join>, 2 spoons, value 1l.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280221-132-victim842" type="victimName">
                  William 
                  Wilson
               <interp inst="t18280221-132-victim842" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
